===Questions===

Yes-no questions are shown with a final particle ''ha''

{|
!Mon
|{{my|<U+1017><U+103E><U+1031><U+103A>}}
|{{my|<U+1005>}}
|{{my|<U+1015><U+102F><U+105A><U+103A>}}
|
|
|{{my|<U+101E><U+1039><U+105A><U+102F>}}
|-
!IPA
|<U+0253><U+00E8> 	
|<U+0283><U+00EC>a 	
|p<U+0259>ng	
|toa		
|ya	
|ha?
|-
!Gloss
|you	
|eat		
|rice	
|com	
|aff	
|q
|}

<U+2018>Have you eaten rice?<U+2019> 

Wh-questions show a different final particle, ''rau''.  The interrogative word does not undergo [[wh-movement]].  That is, it does not necessarily move to the front of the sentence:

{| 
!Mon
|
|{{my|<U+1000><U+103C><U+102C><U+1010><U+103A><U+1000><U+103C><U+1034>}}
|{{my|<U+1019><U+1030>}}
|{{my|<U+101B><U+1031><U+102C>}}
|-
!IPA
|Tala Ong	
|kratkraw	
|mu		
|r<U+00E0>u?
|-
!Gloss
|Tala Ong	
|wash			
|what	
|wh:q
|}
'What did Tala Ong wash?'

